<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Welcome to DashX!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .header { padding: 10px; text-align: center; }
        .content { margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8em; text-align: center; color: #333; padding: 10px; background-color: #B847EF; }
        .button { background-color: #B847EF; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; }
        .legal { color: #666; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.75em; }
        .social-media { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; }
        .social-icon { margin: 0 10px; display: inline-block; }
        .social-icon img { max-width: 24px; }
        a { color: #B847EF; text-decoration: none; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { width: 100%; padding: 10px; }
            .header img { max-width: 100px; height: auto; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/dVzZ2Mdm/photo.jpg" alt="DashX Logo" style="max-width: 200px; height: auto;">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= data %>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to DashX! Your registration was successful, and we are excited to have you on board. We're dedicated to providing you with the best dispatch service experience.</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@dashx.altinsmart.com" class="button">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
        <div class="social-media">
            <a href="https://facebook.com/DashX.logistic" class="social-icon"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/fLJmwXWy/facebook-rounded-large.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/DashX.logistic" class="social-icon"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/G3N2F0n3/instagram-rounded-large.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/DashX.logistic" class="social-icon"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/x1PgJ3NQ/twitter-square-large.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Visit us at: 7B Udeco Medical Road, Chevy View Estate, Lagos</p>
            <p>&copy; [2024] DashX. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
        </div>
        </body>
        </html>
      